snippet.title: 《iOS/Android》DRAGON BALL Z DOKKAN BATTLE: PV (English)
snippet.description: Assemble a team of powerful warriors from a list of familiar faces from the Dragon Ball universe and take part in the earth-shattering battles that have garnered fans across the world! Action that's so intense, your screen might not be able to handle it!
